# Rule 4: Analytics & Monitoring

**Version:** 1.0 (Restructured from former Rule 6)  
**Date:** December 6, 2025  
**Status:** ACTIVE - MANDATORY COMPLIANCE

**Migration Note:** This rule was formerly Rule 6: Advanced Analytics Integration Standards.

---

## Overview

All analytics components within the core_engine must support **real-time processing**, **batch analytics**, **performance attribution**, **regime-aware analysis**, and **multi-timeframe capabilities**.

**Key Principle:** Analytics are a cross-cutting concern that integrate throughout the trading pipeline, providing insights at pre-trade, execution, and post-trade stages.

