## Section 1: Analytics Component Interface

### IAnalyticsComponent Interface

All analytics components MUST implement this interface:

```python
from core_engine.system.interfaces import ISystemComponent
from abc import abstractmethod
from typing import Dict, Any, List, Optional
import pandas as pd
from datetime import datetime

class IAnalyticsComponent(ISystemComponent):
    """Enhanced interface for analytics components"""
    
    @abstractmethod
    async def process_real_time_data(self, data: Dict[str, Any]) -> Dict[str, Any]:
        """Process real-time market data or trading events"""
        pass
    
    @abstractmethod
    async def process_batch_data(
        self, 
        data: pd.DataFrame, 
        start_time: datetime, 
        end_time: datetime
    ) -> Dict[str, Any]:
        """Process historical data in batch mode"""
        pass
    
    @abstractmethod
    async def get_analytics_summary(self, timeframe: str = '1D') -> Dict[str, Any]:
        """Get analytics summary for specified timeframe"""
        pass
    
    @abstractmethod
    async def get_regime_aware_metrics(
        self, 
        regime_context: Dict[str, Any]
    ) -> Dict[str, Any]:
        """Get metrics adjusted for current market regime"""
        pass
    
    @abstractmethod
    async def get_multi_timeframe_analysis(
        self, 
        timeframes: List[str]
    ) -> Dict[str, Dict[str, Any]]:
        """Get analysis across multiple timeframes"""
        pass
```

