## PROHIBITED Analytics Patterns

❌ **Isolated Analytics**: Analytics components must integrate with regime engine  
❌ **Single Timeframe Analysis**: Must support multi-timeframe capabilities  
❌ **Batch-Only Processing**: Must support both real-time and batch processing  
❌ **Non-Attributed Performance**: Must provide strategy-level attribution  
❌ **Static Risk Models**: Must adapt to regime changes  

---

## MANDATORY Analytics Requirements

1. **ISystemComponent Implementation**: All analytics components implement enhanced interface
2. **Real-Time Processing**: Support streaming analytics and event-driven processing
3. **Batch Processing**: Support historical analysis and backtesting
4. **Performance Attribution**: Provide strategy-level and factor-based attribution
5. **Regime Awareness**: Adapt metrics and analysis to market regime conditions
6. **Multi-Timeframe Support**: Analyze across multiple timeframes with correlation analysis

